{"data": [{"id": "4742731", "title": "Income Investing Playbook 2025: Ideas For A New Rate Cycle", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coin graph with percentage signs on top\" data-id=\"2158301114\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>Higher long-term yields and a normalizing yield curve may signal new opportunities for income investors in 2025, even as rate cuts and economic uncertainty shape the market.</p></blockquote> <h2>Introduction to Income Investing</h2> <p>Income investing is a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742731-income-investing-playbook-2025-ideas-new-rate-cycle", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 05:45:00"}, {"id": "4742724", "title": "Bausch + Lomb And Bausch Health: Some Incremental Progress As We Wait For Sale News", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man trapped in the middle of a sea of sharks on chair\" data-id=\"108311069\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mrPliskin/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Overview</h2> <p>As I noted in my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722174-sale-rumors-lift-both-bausch-and-lomb-parent-bausch-health-breakthrough-likely\">last update</a> on <b>Bausch + Lomb Corporation </b>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BLCO\" title=\"Bausch + Lomb Corporation\">BLCO</a></span>) and <strong>Bausch Health Companies Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BHC\" title=\"Bausch Health Companies Inc.\">BHC</a></span>) in September, in which I gave \u201cBuy\u201d ratings to both, the two companies' fates</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742724-bausch-plus-lomb-and-bausch-health-some-incremental-progress-as-we-wait-for-sale-news", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 03:30:16"}, {"id": "4742723", "title": "Cardlytics Continues Revenue Contraction Amid Worsening Economics", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesses use smartphones with online banking digital technology, mobile banking for shopping, payment, finance, bank, account, transfer, credit card, financial and global business online\" data-id=\"2143222197\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Khanchit Khirisutchalual</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Outlook</h2> <p><b>Cardlytics, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CDLX\" title=\"Cardlytics, Inc.\">CDLX</a></span>) beat revenue and earnings estimates in its most recent quarterly <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4258155-cardlytics-non-gaap-eps-of-0_15-beats-0_12-revenue-of-67_06m-beats-9_49m\">financial results</a>.</p> <p>The company helps financial firms in the US and UK market their service offerings digitally with more targeted and profitable</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742723-cardlytics-continues-revenue-contraction-amid-worsening-economics", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 03:03:49"}, {"id": "4742722", "title": "Rhythm Pharmaceuticals: A Key Year Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"corona virus vaccine syringe and graph of stock market in medical health science business blue banner background\" data-id=\"1289907650\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"583px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MadamLead/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today, we put <strong>Rhythm Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RYTM\" title=\"Rhythm Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">RYTM</a></span>)</strong> in the spotlight for the first time since the early <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4610124-rhythm-pharmaceuticals-putting-it-on-the-scale-again\"><strong>summer of 2023</strong></a>. The stock has made a nice move up recently. The company also has several key</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289907650/image_1289907650.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742722-rhythm-pharmaceuticals-a-key-year-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 02:49:19"}, {"id": "4742720", "title": "Hercules Capital: Are The Dividends Safe? I'm Buying!", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pomnik Alexander\" data-id=\"638002212\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1040px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">benjaminec/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Hercules Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HTGC\" title=\"Hercules Capital, Inc.\">HTGC</a></span>) is a business development company concentrating on (mostly) US businesses operating within a few key sectors:</p> <ul> <li>Technology.</li> <li>Life sciences.</li> <li>SaaS.</li> <li>Sustainable and renewable technology.</li> </ul> <p>It offers attractive income to its shareholders (~10% yield</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742720-hercules-capital-are-the-dividends-safe-im-buying", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 02:31:25"}, {"id": "4742719", "title": "Regeneron: Recent Bear Run May Be Justified -- Pharma Faces A Testing 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"An up close picture of report card grades\" data-id=\"172413295\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jaker5000</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Overview</h2> <p>So far this year, I have covered <b>Regeneron Pharmaceuticals, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/REGN\" title=\"Regeneron Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">REGN</a></span>), the New York based Pharma giant, on two occasions. In <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4661781-why-i-expect-regeneron-to-keep-delivering-for-investors-in-2024-upgrade\">January</a>, I used detailed financial modelling to suggest that Regeneron stock was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742719-regeneron-recent-bear-run-may-be-justified-pharma-faces-a-testing-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 02:28:05"}, {"id": "4742718", "title": "MidCap Financial: 11% Yield, 86% Payout Ratio, NAV Discount (Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesspeople walking on painted up going graph, on asphalt\" data-id=\"912018754\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>MidCap Financial Investment Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MFIC\" title=\"MidCap Financial Investment Corporation\">MFIC</a></span>)</strong> is a well-managed, consistently profitable business development company with stable dividend payout metrics.</p> <p>In the last quarter, MidCap Financial Investment paid passive income investors a special $0.20 per share dividend in addition to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742718-midcap-financial-11-percent-yield-86-percent-payout-ratio-nav-discount-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 02:23:41"}, {"id": "4742717", "title": "ZIM Integrated Shipping: The Return Of The Fat Dividend", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Truck carrying forty-foot container leaving port terminal with ship and quay crane on the background. Seaport operation activities, container shipping, and logistics.\" data-id=\"2157040201\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/u